# tests/

Comprehensive BATS (Bash Automated Testing System) test suite for the Intent CLI tool. Includes unit tests for individual commands, integration tests for complete workflows, and test infrastructure with helper utilities. Currently 327 tests passing across 17 test files.

## Dirs

- `fixtures/` -- Test fixtures and sample files used by test cases
- `integration/` -- End-to-end integration tests validating complete workflows
- `lib/` -- Test helper functions and setup utilities (test_helper.bash)
- `unit/` -- Unit tests for individual Intent commands organized by domain

## Files

- `run_tests.sh` -- Main test runner script that executes BATS tests with colored output and status reporting
- `README.md` -- Test suite documentation with structure, prerequisites, and test writing guidelines
